data.description: This is a unique opportunity to rent this completely renovated top-to-the-bottom house for your family to enjoy living in a suburbian luxury. Everything is new and designed with modern standards of the executive lifestyle. Open floor plan connecting inside and outside, the gourmet kitchen made for entertaining, inground pool and pool house, 6 bedrooms including two suites, one of which is one main floor. Moorestown is the best small town to live with great schools and a convenient location close to all major highways. 2021-02-25
